{"tid":1843052,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"連大陸都限制湖北人，香港封關等幾時？","createTime":"2020-01-26T04:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T11:37:42.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4cff9037783f219e0b7c4796a799a7894e22f6c","tid":1843052,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/20200125h2.jpg?itok=zLlVBoCm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F20200125h2.jpg%3Fitok%3DzLlVBoCm&h=e1529e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大袁國勇教授警告，未來幾日係防止「新沙士」社區爆發的「最後機會」。雖然他沒有講明，但係人都知佢唔單止講緊戴口罩，而係暗地批評緊特區政府邊境防疫不足。<br />\n<br />\n單單年卅晚一天，就有36,705大陸人循海陸空入境香港，更恐怖的是，勸極都仲有20幾萬香港居民唔識死返大陸（圖）。<br />\n<br />\n「新沙士」早期病徵輕微，靠邊境測體溫或填健康問卷難以堵截帶病毒人士。<br />\n<br />\n眼前剩三個可能：<br />\n1）仿效大陸城市，對所有來自湖北的人進行隔離醫學觀察（上圖）；<br />\n2）仿效台灣採取局部限制，禁止所有湖北人入境；<br />\n3）全面禁止所有在大陸的人士入境，包括香港居民<br />\n<br />\n1）涉及大量額外醫護，地方也不夠；現在應在2）和3）之間選一個程度施限。剩下的時間不多了。<br />\n<br />\n正查詢36,705名來港大陸人中，有多少來自湖北。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸<br />\n新界西立法會議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070233&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=9951e31c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070233&h=f6ce5d12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070233</a>"},{"pid":"fb7acd6f67a018d1900bed9cf144af7d9f9d1924","tid":1843052,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/VeZt3xV.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1月20日患者與女兒共進一餐，次日回港</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"0274a297e35a97f818003613eabcdd4e5d07a72e","tid":1843052,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都係避難所,有病落黎避,殺完人返黎避"}]}